                       INSTALLING SPLAT

Splat can be compiled and ran on Linux, Mac OS X, and Windows. At
the moment no install packages are available, see "packaging" for manual
install instructions


Running
-------
From tar-ball:
  Extract tar-ball into desired location, and run the fallowing command.
    'java -Djava.library.path=./ -jar Splat-0.0.0.jar'

From source:
  From root directory run the fallowing command. Note: requires buildr
  to be installed.
    'buildr run'


Compiling
---------
From root directory run the fallowing command. Will compile into 'target'
Note: requires buildr to be installed.
  'buildr compile'

Packaging
---------
To build a tar-ball, from root directory run the fallowing command. Will
build into 'target'. See 'Running' for instruction to run from tar-ball.
Note: requires buildr to be installed.
  'buildr package'

